column1: Diabetes is the binary dependent variable in this dataset with categories — pos/neg. We have the following eight independent variables
Glucose: Plasma glucose concentration (glucose tolerance test)
Mass: Body mass index (weight in Kg/ (height in m)² )

column10: R.S. (1988). Using the ADAP learning algorithm to forecast the onset of diabetes mellitus. In Proceedings of the Symposium on Computer Applications and Medical Care (pp. 261--265). IEEE Computer Society Press.
